Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.94,0:01:53.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop, Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.95,0:02:04.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's happened, Kohaku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.23,0:02:10.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The thread...of a spider!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.73,0:02:15.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.57,0:02:18.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.45,0:02:37.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.06,0:02:39.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ko... ha... ku?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.46,0:02:40.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.63,0:02:43.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.43,0:02:45.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.43,0:02:50.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A white baboon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.93,0:02:51.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.47,0:02:53.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's Naraku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.91,0:02:56.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tell me in detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:02:59.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The slain bodies of\ncountless villagers...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:03:01.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and the half-demon who\nattacked them...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.58,0:03:03.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,His name is Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.31,0:03:06.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha seeks the power of\nthe Sacred Jewel...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.75,0:03:09.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to turn himself into a\nfull-fledged demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.02,0:03:11.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sacred Jewel?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.69,0:03:14.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He must have believed that he\nwould find the Jewel at the village...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.03,0:03:17.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and thus attacked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.16,0:03:20.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.66,0:03:24.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Give me my weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:27.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will get the one who\nattacked my village...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.84,0:03:30.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will kill this half-demon\NInuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:42.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A horse cannot make it\nfrom here on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.13,0:03:54.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango... is dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:04:00.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No way! Until I get that Inuyasha,\NI'll not die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.40,0:04:02.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.74,0:04:05.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But can you fight decently\nin that condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.24,0:04:11.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Slaying demons is\nmy profession.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.65,0:04:15.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you can't be stopped?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.09,0:04:23.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well then, I will send Naraku\nwith you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.66,0:04:25.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He is my advisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:29.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's very familiar with demons\nand should prove useful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.36,0:04:31.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.53,0:04:34.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,when your mission is complete,\ncome back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.57,0:04:38.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You have lost your family and\nall your fellow villagers...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:40.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am much saddened for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.31,0:04:43.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will never return.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:46.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I do not have much\ntime left.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.88,0:04:51.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please...my body...\nhold up a little longer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.09,0:04:53.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Until I complete my\nfinal task.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.00,0:05:05.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The cave where the Sacred\NJewel was created?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.23,0:05:08.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes. We are headed now to\nthe outskirts of the village...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:09.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to the limestone cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.51,0:05:14.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Actually, this village served as\na sort of factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.41,0:05:15.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Factory?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.51,0:05:18.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They made weapons and armor from\nthe skins and bones...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.65,0:05:21.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,of the demons that were slain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:30.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And unused portions were disposed of\nin this cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.03,0:05:36.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hence, this limestone cave is filled\nwith the remains of demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.16,0:05:39.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And it seems that deep inside\nthe cave was once...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.03,0:05:41.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,full of carcasses of demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.60,0:05:44.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's where the Sacred Jewel was?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.47,0:05:48.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes... that is the story that has been\npassed down in this region.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:51.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good work, Myoga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.71,0:05:53.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you for the compliment!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.88,0:05:57.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I did my best in the hope that\nit would be of help to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.22,0:05:59.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.22,0:06:01.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When you stay by me,\nyou're always in danger...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:03.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so I thought you just\nran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.09,0:06:06.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Inuyasha, how could you\nthink that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.93,0:06:08.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:10.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shall we go in?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.73,0:06:12.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right... let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.57,0:06:14.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just a minute, Master Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.34,0:06:15.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.84,0:06:23.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A strong barrier has been placed\nat the entrance...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.91,0:06:25.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and one cannot just walk in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.18,0:06:28.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then say so earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.03,0:06:40.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,S-sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.70,0:06:42.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:46.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.04,0:06:52.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you in pain, Sango?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.08,0:06:56.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.01,0:06:58.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pitiful thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.31,0:07:01.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But you won't be able to rest in peace\neven if you died.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.55,0:07:03.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Would you care to try this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.82,0:07:04.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.99,0:07:06.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,a Sacred Jewel fragment!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:11.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why are you in possession of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:13.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just who?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.79,0:07:16.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have had this from\nlong before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.40,0:07:18.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am willing to lend\nit to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:19.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.70,0:07:23.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You may believe that the\NSacred Jewel is used only for evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:25.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But there are good uses for it as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:31.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.58,0:07:33.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:35.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.25,0:07:36.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's no way into the cave...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.92,0:07:40.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and everyone who could've\ntalked to us has been killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:42.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.72,0:07:43.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.59,0:07:47.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The more skilled Slayers went\nto some castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.60,0:07:49.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.93,0:07:51.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If those men had been in the village...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.10,0:07:55.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,they would easily have turned back\nan attack by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.27,0:07:58.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right... Let's go to that castle...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:03.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and talk to the men about the\nsecret of the Sacred Jewel...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:06.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and find out how to get into\nthat cave... easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.82,0:08:10.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now then, let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:16.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hurry, Kagome!\NOr we'll leave you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.29,0:08:19.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.63,0:08:26.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Myoga...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.30,0:08:29.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,is the castle this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:30.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.77,0:08:34.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Inuyasha, were you walking\nwithout knowing which way to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.11,0:08:37.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?! Err... You didn't say a word...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.55,0:08:39.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so I figured I was going\nthe right way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.88,0:08:40.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.98,0:08:43.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the castle shouldn't be too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.22,0:08:46.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can't you sniff it out\nfrom here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.25,0:08:50.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh... I can't get a whiff\nof anything here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.93,0:08:52.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:08.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You are Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.28,0:09:11.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will slay you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.61,0:09:14.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.32,0:09:15.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:16.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Someone from the village?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:17.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.05,0:09:20.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You must not cross swords\nwith Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:21.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hiraikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.96,0:09:24.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This ain't the time to say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.20,0:09:30.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tetsusaiga is losing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:31.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.04,0:09:39.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why do you come after me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.37,0:09:40.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Silence, half-demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.67,0:09:42.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will avenge everyone\nfrom my village!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.08,0:09:47.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Old Myoga! What's she saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.21,0:09:48.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have no idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.75,0:09:50.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Inuyasha, it's coming again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:54.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We must do something about\nthat weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.76,0:09:55.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Agreed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:09:57.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.46,0:10:00.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:04.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look! Naraku's poison insects!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.47,0:10:06.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, Miroku!\NYou suck them in, you'll be poisoned!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.74,0:10:09.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-why are they here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:10.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.61,0:10:14.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.94,0:10:19.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, give up and\nlet her slay you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.05,0:10:20.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.05,0:10:22.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not in a hundred years!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.46,0:10:30.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am your opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.62,0:10:33.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you! Interfere and\NI'll kill you first!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.96,0:10:34.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.13,0:10:37.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You may have said those words\nwhen you killed my people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.07,0:10:39.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I'll not die so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:43.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She believes that Inuyasha\nattacked the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.64,0:10:45.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's being deceived by Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:51.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}She has a Sacred Jewel\nfragment in her back!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.85,0:10:55.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Before that weapon returns!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.02,0:10:56.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Poison Powder!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.15,0:10:58.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A miasma!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.85,0:11:03.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demons with ears like yours have\na weakness against strong scents!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.86,0:11:04.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't get close!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.93,0:11:08.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Leave it to a Demon Slayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:12.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, well... if it isn't the monk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:15.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku... die now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.60,0:11:20.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't. Not until I gather all\nthe Sacred Jewel fragments.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.88,0:11:23.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't know what you are\nscheming, but it's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.23,0:11:41.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.90,0:11:44.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.14,0:11:53.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is not for the\nlikes of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.11,0:11:56.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now that I have the fragment\nin my possession...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.14,0:11:57.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I need not to linger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.24,0:11:58.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku... why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.95,0:12:01.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Farewell, Monk...\nand Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.02,0:12:03.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Why you...!\N- You won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.92,0:12:11.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango... I await you at the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.09,0:12:16.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kill Inuyasha without fail\nand return.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.86,0:12:20.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naraku... Can I really trust him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.27,0:12:24.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.27,0:12:25.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.47,0:12:29.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara, follow him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.98,0:12:32.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If he does anything strange,\nkill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.22,0:12:40.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.39,0:12:41.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop, Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.09,0:12:47.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha! I will fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:49.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You will die right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:51.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you still saying that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:54.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must kill him now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.07,0:12:56.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before my life wanes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.57,0:13:01.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:05.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.88,0:13:09.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Without your weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.75,0:13:10.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Poison Powder!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:16.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}My poison shield mask!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.33,0:13:21.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is he up to?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.60,0:13:23.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}H- he's...not trying to save me?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.93,0:13:25.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, he isn't!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.10,0:13:29.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's the enemy who attacked\nmy village!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:32.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:37.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You! Haven't you realized yet that\NNaraku is tricking you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.88,0:13:41.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And... you're covered with blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.78,0:13:42.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.29,0:13:50.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l-I didn't know it was this bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.29,0:13:53.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I didn't feel any pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.86,0:13:57.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.50,0:13:58.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:07.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku, are you afraid about\nbecoming a Slayer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.41,0:14:10.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,N-no...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.65,0:14:14.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku... this is just between\nyou and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:17.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There isn't a soul who's not\nafraid of fighting a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.09,0:14:18.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:20.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then, you too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.12,0:14:23.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yup... not only me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.26,0:14:25.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Father and all the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:28.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But we're not fighting alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.03,0:14:30.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're always together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:32.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We fight together with our comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.87,0:14:35.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So it'll be okay, since we're\nwith everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.54,0:14:37.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.04,0:14:43.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sister... I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.88,0:14:45.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:48.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is she dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:50.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She just fainted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.55,0:14:55.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, she has a Sacred Jewel\nfragment imbedded in her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:56.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:15:00.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I knew from the scent of her blood\nthat she was badly injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:04.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That Naraku... He used the\NSacred Jewel...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.47,0:15:06.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to make her fight until\nshe died.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.84,0:15:10.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No way will I lose him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.41,0:15:20.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thanks... you're gonna give\nme a ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.38,0:15:25.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.87,0:15:44.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't take me lightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.57,0:15:46.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-why... you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.37,0:15:49.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.98,0:15:53.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.88,0:15:58.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.29,0:16:00.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have no voice!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.72,0:16:01.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}My body won't move!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.72,0:16:04.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's wrong with me?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.06,0:16:10.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Someone's back... Warm.\NWhose... ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.17,0:16:14.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.17,0:16:16.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Conscious, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.30,0:16:18.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Put me down! What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.17,0:16:19.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:21.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're going after Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.58,0:16:23.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He took our Sacred Jewel fragment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:26.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your name's Sango, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.31,0:16:28.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Keep bothering me, and\NI'll leave you right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.72,0:16:29.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.58,0:16:33.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha! You're so rude!\NNo wonder people misjudge you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.92,0:16:38.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Forgive him. He talks rough,\nbut he's actually quite nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:39.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.03,0:16:43.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango, Master Inuyasha and the others\ncould not leave you to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.53,0:16:45.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,with your deep wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:46.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Old Myoga...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.67,0:16:47.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's speed it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.64,0:16:53.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naraku... You won't get away!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.65,0:17:02.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is Naraku's appearance\na deception?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.85,0:17:06.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Deception or not...\nfind out for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.73,0:17:16.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! No matter I slash them,\nthey revert back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.20,0:17:24.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He'll impale me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:28.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:30.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you doing?!\NYou're hopeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.88,0:17:32.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.08,0:17:38.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, so you're still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.65,0:17:41.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As if a human can kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.09,0:17:46.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You looked to be losing to\nthat wounded Slayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.69,0:17:47.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:49.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku, you're the one, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.76,0:17:51.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You turned the pack of demons\non the village...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.03,0:17:53.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and annihilated everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.53,0:17:56.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I just told the demons that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.77,0:17:58.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the guard on the village\nwas down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.91,0:18:00.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}So he...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.91,0:18:03.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Was your goal to get the fragments\nkept at the village?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.08,0:18:05.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh? Very perceptive of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:08.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I must say where there's\na Sacred Jewel fragment...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.55,0:18:10.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,there's always a fight to\nbe found.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.29,0:18:13.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,For just that...\nyou killed so many?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.52,0:18:15.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.79,0:18:16.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.36,0:18:19.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The demons in the castle...\nthe demon spider...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.06,0:18:21.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Were they all part of\nyour trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.56,0:18:22.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.76,0:18:25.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that what you call\njust simple games?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.10,0:18:29.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I thought that the Slayer\nof this village...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.54,0:18:31.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,could handle any sort\nof demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.61,0:18:34.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:37.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.75,0:18:39.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.88,0:18:45.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No way I loan the Sacred Jewel\nto one who defies me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:46.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:49.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The fragment suppressed\nthe pain...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:50.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.93,0:18:55.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You should have believed Inuyasha\nwas your sworn enemy and killed him...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:57.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,then you would have died happily.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.47,0:19:00.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}F- father...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.40,0:19:04.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.94,0:19:08.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You always trample on\npeople's feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.74,0:19:11.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you remembering Kikyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.61,0:19:13.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup! You son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.62,0:19:22.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.06,0:19:28.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Too easy... Could this really be the\NNaraku I was pursuing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.60,0:19:33.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A punk like this... made Kikyo suffer...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.90,0:19:36.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,as well as countless others.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.10,0:19:38.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.58,0:19:44.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,His body is moving freely!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.75,0:19:47.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will not die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.01,0:19:49.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,His head is alive too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.32,0:19:50.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.03,0:20:01.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's reverting back to himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.20,0:20:04.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's using the power of\nthe Sacred Jewel!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.97,0:20:06.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why didn't I notice it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.20,0:20:08.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I spent time with such a demon...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.14,0:20:11.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}yet I sensed nothing at all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.11,0:20:14.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}In fact, even now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.94,0:20:18.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}No! I can't sense any\ndemon spirit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.88,0:20:20.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then...he{\i0} is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.85,0:20:22.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha! That's just a\ndemon puppet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.35,0:20:24.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A puppet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.52,0:20:27.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In demon puppetry, the true\napparition is hidden...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.55,0:20:29.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,in the deepest part of the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.36,0:20:31.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,His heart!\NAim straight for his heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.56,0:20:33.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Humph... so you figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.40,0:20:38.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.07,0:20:49.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.02,0:20:57.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.32,0:21:00.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is demon puppetry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.32,0:21:03.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This paper wrapped around the doll\nbelongs to Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.12,0:21:06.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then who was it that\nwe fought all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.93,0:21:08.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A counterfeit Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.06,0:21:13.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Probably the real Naraku was\nsomewhere safe controlling this puppet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.01,0:21:24.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Young Lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.21,0:21:28.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Neither the girl-Slayer nor\NNaraku have returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.95,0:21:31.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Could they have been killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.45,0:21:33.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That is possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.12,0:21:36.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Continue a strict guard\naround the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.16,0:21:37.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, Sire.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.66,0:21:45.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This castle...and this body which\nhides my true identity...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.83,0:21:49.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will use to great satisfaction...\nmy dear Kagemaki.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.89,0:23:50.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sacred Jewel is also known as\N"Jewel of Four Souls."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.02,0:23:55.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How did the souls form a jewel\nwith the power the demons covet?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.03,0:23:58.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Deep in the cave\nnear the Slayer' village...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.77,0:24:00.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,lies a priestess's mummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.33,0:24:03.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She was killed in a battle\nhundreds of years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.34,0:24:07.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Sacred Jewel's glint awakens\na gigantic monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.74,0:24:11.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next, "Secret of the Jewel\nof Four Souls Revealed".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.91,0:24:13.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look forward to it!
